name: Devil's Excalibur
description:
It is to be said that only the chosen could pull out the sword from the stone. One of which was named Excalibur which belonged to King Arther as an Arthurian legend.

I a demon believe that this sword was meant to be picked up by the Devil (Lucifer) to fight his Brother in a war we call Apocalypse*.

Software used - Blender.
Resolution - 3840x2160

*Everything said here is a single person's imagination.
